    "title": "Vacancy for Teacher at Lovely Professional University",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Lovely Professional University. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Teacher to strengthen our Navi Mumbai-based team.\n\nAbout Lovely Professional University:\nLovely Professional University is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Zoom/Teams\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Lovely Professional University!",
